column5: Glen and I are going out at 9am (SAT), on Georgian Bay. If someone wants to join us we have room for a third. Need to be at my house in Penetang 9am...I'll be up 'till midnight..send me a PM  Wayne
Nobody??? ..... tell your wife you got called in for OT !!
Hey wayne how long would it take me to get to penetange...from oshawa????  oh ya the boss said i could go she wants me too
Your back shouldn't be making the trip though...I don't wanna be the "reason" you're lame for the next few months!  2hrs! 2hr-15
LAST CALL...my eyes are gettin heavy....
Do you do fly by shootings pick up and drop off.  Have a good day fishin.
NO pick ups Mike...floats are half off the plane.  Nighty nite lads....I hope tomorrow Glen and I can make ya feel sorry for not saying "Hell yah" !

Hey Wayne I would love to get out with you somtime in the future before you put that trusty Lund in storage for the winter. I wish i would have seen this post a little sooner.   If you get out in the next few weeks drop me a PM i would be happy to join you. Mike
I'm still here Mike...if you can make Penetang by 9.. you're in!
